snippet.title: Prison Boss VR - Official Trailer | Upload VR Showcase Winter 2023
snippet.description: Prison Boss VR is available now on PS VR2, and the sequel in co-op, Prison Boss Prohibition, is coming soon. Check out the trailer to see quirky characters and more from this crafting and trading game that turns your VR space into a jail cell. In Prison Boss VR, craft cigarettes, alcohol, and cookies for other inmates! Customize your cell as your reputation grows! Earn cash until you can’t store it anymore and become the Prison Boss.
